videos.description: LSU's Tremont Waters tosses up an alley-oop to Marlon Taylor, who leaps over a Florida defender's back to throw it down.
videos.headline: Taylor jumps over defender's back for dunk

videos.description: Florida's Jalen Hudson drives to the basket to slam home an aggressive dunk.
videos.headline: Hudson creates his own lane to jam it

videos.description: Andrew Nembhard alley-oops it to Keyontae Johnson to tie the game up at 64-64 in the final minutes.
videos.headline: Johnson ties it for Florida on alley-oop

videos.description: Jalen Hudson comes away with the steal, then slams it on the other end to make it a 1-point game in the final minute of regulation.
videos.headline: LSU turns it over, Florida capitalizes in final minute of regulation

videos.description: Florida takes the lead on Jalen Hudson's 3-pointer, but LSU's Tremont Waters lays it in on the other end to tie it and force overtime.
videos.headline: Florida takes lead, LSU ties it in final seconds to force OT

videos.description: Florida has trouble getting a shot off in the waning seconds of overtime and falls to LSU 79-78.
videos.headline: Florida can't get off final shot in OT, falls to LSU
